overview: Music Video For OSEES' Scum Show album: A Foul Form. This film was shot at Le Trianon in Paris during OSEES' show on June 29th 2022, on Tri-x Super8 with a Canon 514 XL-S and a GAF 415 XLM. The reels were hand processed at the Collective Lab L'Etna. The film was pre-edited and animated, colored, and special effects were also processed by hand; digitally edited. With the Kind Courtesy of Le Trianon, Paris All done by Malo sutra Fish Long live Punk Spirit!
title: Scum Show
